{"tid":283600,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"3DS芒亨畫面係好PSP少少 但已經唔係嗰回事","createTime":"2017-06-14T09:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T03:02:48.000Z","uid":9767,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0906f55cb50a70aeb6d55248448721f8148fd8","tid":283600,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:37:48.000Z","msg":"當年2008年2G 依加睇返係幾樣衰畫面 但嗰時算幾靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我由PSP 2G直跳3DS MHXX 但宜家係2017年 啲畫面進步程度已經可以忽略 因為十年時間你只係俾啲咁嘅野我 有領你野嘅感覺 至少起格呢點真心難接受囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過MHXX係幾好玩 呢點無得否認 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a054b2cc5d99989e1f0fa017036146fb9d0a58","tid":283600,"uid":10140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T10:11:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年2008年2G 依加睇返係幾樣衰畫面 但嗰時算幾靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我由PSP 2G直跳3DS MHXX 但宜家係2017年 啲畫面進步程度已經可以忽略 因為十年時間你只係俾啲咁嘅野我 有領你野嘅感覺 <span style=\"color: red;\">至少起格呢點真心難接受囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n不過MHXX係幾好玩 呢點無得否認 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1 等NS版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bd5731985ed926e6835bb6ac164c51ba855576","tid":283600,"uid":45536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:15:10.000Z","msg":"點解無玩到P3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c9c607578cdcf38d3f6be1e148a8179bb5ab59","tid":283600,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:38:49.000Z","msg":"開3d先正"},{"pid":"61366bd0fcc698cc5f4b7977c0ec2a0f3043dd7b","tid":283600,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:53:18.000Z","msg":"3DS係2011年出<br />\n係第一部裸眼3D遊戲機<br />\n玩過最靚畫質係Biohazard<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/104103_3a218aba4e5e83ab3dfb7c9def227b2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F104103_3a218aba4e5e83ab3dfb7c9def227b2d.jpg&h=42814fab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果玩過呢隻game會發現<br />\n係可以做到好多360/PS3 game既畫面特效<br />\n<br />\n但缺點係個mon解像度低<br />\n<br />\nMH要顧online四打有足夠流暢度<br />\n所以畫質要比單機隻Biohazard大降<br />\n<br />\nMHXX好彩冇買3DS版<br />\n轉頭8月就出Switch版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n720p又貼圖清好多<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/104745_04472dc32f5f28f5223f2e22c4231c40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F104745_04472dc32f5f28f5223f2e22c4231c40.jpg&h=9b8799d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nE3隻MH World變左似Dino Crysis<br />\n獵人走左入侏羅紀公園<br />\n感覺上完全就歐美玩家口味而大改<br />\n不過難得Capcom肯試新野<br />\n都好過日本風MH再不斷食老本"},{"pid":"82dae4680bca8ab943400df5530bc3318e8b0fe6","tid":283600,"uid":10433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"之前為mhx出3ds 一開game真係好似番左psp年代咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998f8145d1b0c78c1d1b39db3dc78c034b0366a6","tid":283600,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T03:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前為mhx出3ds 一開game真係好似番左psp年代咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇開3D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}